descriptionHtml:
Start your engines, Uplanders! The Upland Racing App has arrived. It’s time to conquer the streets of Upland and burn some rubber as you scorch the race track. Get a front row seat to view races all around Upland, including your own past races. Get all the details with a full list of circuits, fastest lap times, weather conditions, car make and model, driver name, and so much more. Download TODAY and get down on some awesome racing action. It’s Upland. It’s racing. It’s BOTH!

The Upland Racing App is an accessory app to the Upland Metaverse Super App and real estate simulation game available on Google Play.
Install the Upland App now and enjoy a 4,500 UPX sign-up bonus!!
